<< after much camping, >>

Much camping??? Much Camping???????? You reported about 21 hours max on it.
Let's see...Runnyeye was no time for me. Goblin alchemist in Misty Thicket

hours and still waiting. And I know several monks out there have beaten me
in time (wish them dern iksar scaled gloves were less of weight).
